### Test the top performers API with default limit (10)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employee-performance/top-performers?startDate=01/01/2025&endDate=01/05/2025

### Test the top performers API with custom limit (5)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employee-performance/top-performers?startDate=01/01/2025&endDate=01/05/2025&limit=5

### Test with a different date range (1 month)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employee-performance/top-performers?startDate=01/04/2025&endDate=01/05/2025&limit=3

### Test with a longer date range (3 months)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employee-performance/top-performers?startDate=01/01/2025&endDate=01/04/2025&limit=5
